The new TaxiClub application will help you book a taxi all over Moldova. A user-friendly application interface will help you easily place an order. It is designed for users of all ages to help them get the right information in any kind of situations. Get rid of the waste of time for explanations, where to meet you and where the destination point is. Just use one of the currently available options:
- address selection from the built-in catalog;
- search for the address on the Google Maps or/and Yandex Maps;
- book a car by pointing on the map.
Get permanent updates regarding  your order on the smartphone screen:
- distance from the start address to the destination point;
- the preliminary cost of the order;
- current status of the order;
- data on the assigned car;
- final check of the trip.
If necessary, use the option to communicate with the driver directly from the application.
Your choice is important for us, so we strive to improve your comfort when using our taxi services. Try the mobile application to call a taxi and make sure each of our interactions will become even more convenient and pleasant.

GAL trans is a Moldovan carrier company that operates regular bus services from Moldova to Romania, Ukraine and Russia.

With the application from GAL Trans you can easily:
– choose a flight suitable for the requested date;
– check buses routes on the map;
– see buses’ photos;
– make a reservation with payment to the driver during the boarding;
– pay for the ticket online;
– get access to the history of all purchased tickets in the personal account
– make a quick ticket return in your personal account
– request information from support service.

GAL Trans has a large bus fleet that meets European standards.

The professional drivers team will make sure that your trip is as comfortable as possible.

GAL Trans - it's important, who you travel with!

INFOBUS is an application to search and purchase bus, train and plane tickets.

You can use INFOBUS for the following:
- book and buy tickets in just a few clicks without leaving home;
- check flight schedules online;
- always have tickets with you;
- automatically receive bonuses upon payment of a ticket.

Key Features:

Convenience - user-friendly interface;
Time saving – the application saves your time, so you could spend it on yourself :)
Efficiency – the ticket is immediately sent to your email upon payment;
Simplicity – easy-to-use search, booking and payment system;
Information content - the application contains up-to-date information on seats availability on flights, luggage transportation features, current prices and discounts, etc.;
Systematic updates – the application is constantly updated and supplemented with new information and features for the convenience of our customers.


We created this application to make your life easier.

INFOBUS
